    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础的序列图，描述客户端和服务器之间的交互。先确定两个参与者吧，一个叫Client，一个叫Server。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Client和Server作为两个参与者。Client是发起请求的一方，Server是响应方，这个理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个关系。先搭好这个骨架，后续我们再补充具体的请求和响应消息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，Client在左边，Server在右边，两条生命线都拉出来了。你看看这个布局可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "布局没问题。不过我在想，Client和Server的命名要不要用中文？还是保持英文？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "建议保持英文Client和Server，这样和技术文档保持一致。如果后面需要中文显示，可以用别名as语法，比如participant Client as 客户端。你觉得呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
